Deferred Compensation
The Company has deferred compensation plans which permit certain employees and executives to defer a portion of
their salary, bonus, certain other incentive awards and retirement contributions. Participants can diversify these
amounts among 23 investment funds including a Boeing stock unit account.
Total expense related to deferred compensation was $126, $93 and $174 in 2021, 2020 and 2019, respectively. As of
December 31, 2021 and 2020, the deferred compensation liability which is being marked to market was $1,703 and
$1,718.
